                          </span>
                       </div>
                       <p className="text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-500 truncate mb-1">{asset.url}</p>
                       <p className="text-[9px] text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600 font-medium italic line-clamp-2 leading-relaxed">"{asset.detectionReasoning || 'Decoding visual patterns...'}"</p>
